The possible values for $x$ and $y$ are between 0 and 1, inclusive.
The region of the number line that satisfies $x < y < 2x$ is the shaded region below:

[asy]
draw((0,0)--(1,0));
fill((0,0)--(1,0)--(1,1)--(0.5,1)--(0,0.5)--cycle, gray(0.7));
draw((0,0)--(1,1));
